      <title>尽管不良贷款增加，HDFC 银行利润仍增长 2.2%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/hdfc-bank-posts-profit-growth-in-line-with-analyst-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最大的私营部门贷款机构 HDFC 银行公布第三季度利润符合市场预期，尽管其不良贷款总额有所增加。]]></description>
